**Key implementation details:**
- PreDeduct uses `SELECT ... FOR UPDATE` for atomic row-level locking, pre-deducts 30 min at combined A+B leg rate
- AcquireSlot uses Redis INCR with rollback on limit exceeded
- Finalize calculates A-leg (6s blocks) and B-leg (60s blocks) costs, reconciles diff with refund/charge

